---
layout: layouts/standard.njk
title: "Notebook — Cavero Diego"
description: "Process notes, workshop reflections and visual references from the Cavero Diego project."
section: campo
footerOmit: campo
lang: en
langBtn: true
pageStyle: |
  /* Nav background comes from global.css */

  /* ─── Header ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .cuaderno-header {
    padding: 18vh 8vw 8vh;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-10);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 4vw;
  }
  .cuaderno-eyebrow {
    font-size: .64rem; letter-spacing: .3em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--stone);
    display: block; margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }
  .cuaderno-title {
    font-family: 'Boska', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 7rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: .95;
    letter-spacing: -.02em;
  }
  .cuaderno-header-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: .4rem;
  }
  .cuaderno-header-desc {
    max-width: 34ch;
    font-size: .86rem;
    color: var(--stone);
    line-height: 1.85;
    text-align: right;
  }

  /* ─── Empty state ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .cuaderno-empty {
    padding: 16vh 8vw;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 1.8rem;
  }
  .cuaderno-empty-label {
    font-size: .58rem;
    letter-spacing: .3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--stone);
    opacity: .5;
  }
  .cuaderno-empty-text {
    font-family: 'Boska', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--stone);
    opacity: .35;
    max-width: 28ch;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  /* ─── Responsive ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .cuaderno-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .cuaderno-header-right { align-items: flex-start; }
    .cuaderno-header-desc { text-align: left; }
  }
---

<!-- ─── HEADER ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<header class="cuaderno-header">
  <div class="cuaderno-header-left">
    <span class="cuaderno-eyebrow">Cavero Diego</span>
    <h1 class="cuaderno-title">Notebook</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="cuaderno-header-right">
    <p class="cuaderno-header-desc">
      Notes on territory, process and materials.
      What we see, what we learn and what inspires us while building the brand.
    </p>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ─── EMPTY STATE ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<main class="cuaderno-empty">
  <span class="cuaderno-empty-label">Coming Soon</span>
  <p class="cuaderno-empty-text">
    The first entry is on its way.<br>
    Meanwhile, work continues in the workshop.
  </p>
</main>
